INSTALLING

just "make", then "sudo make install" if you want to
you must have libasound installed (ALSA libraries) on linux. check out the package management system on your distro
if you want only the client or the server, you can use the makefiles in the corresponding directories
you might want to make an init script for the server

USAGE

dsra --help
dsra-server --help 

:P

